1 A BILL for an Act to create and enact a new section to chapter 15-10 of the North Dakota
2 Century Code, relating to the prohibition of academic tenure at two-year colleges.
3 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY OF NORTH DAKOTA:
4 SECTION 1. A new section to chapter 15-10 of the North Dakota Century Code is created
5 and enacted as follows:
6 Academic tenure prohibited at two - year colleges .
7 A faculty member is not eligible for academic tenure, if the faculty member is hired after
8 July 1, 2026, and employed at a two - year college in the state. For purposes of this section, a
9 two - year college is any of the following: Bismarck state college, Dakota college at Bottineau ,
10 Lake Region state college, North Dakota state college of science, and Williston state college.
